                    Complete Blood Count (CBC):
                </div>
                <p>The Complete Blood Count (CBC) is a fundamental test that assesses the composition and health of your blood.
                     It provides crucial information about your red blood cells, white blood cells, and 
                     platelets, helping to diagnose a wide range of conditions such as anemia, infections, 
                     and blood disorders. By evaluating the levels of different blood components, the CBC 
                     gives our medical experts valuable insights into your overall health, aiding in timely
                      diagnosis and appropriate treatment recommendations. Whether you're visiting us for a
                       routine check-up or seeking answers to specific health concerns, our comprehensive CBC analysis
                        plays a pivotal role in understanding your body's internal dynamics.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="./images/sample-tube.png" alt="" height="250px">
                </div>  

        </div>

        <div class="test">
