                <div class="large">
                    X-ray Imaging:
                </div>
                <p>X-ray imaging is a fundamental and time-tested diagnostic technique that provides
                     quick and informative snapshots of the body's internal structures. Using small amounts
                      of radiation, X-rays capture detailed images of bones, tissues, and organs, aiding in
                       the diagnosis of a variety of conditions, from fractures and lung infections to dental issues. 
                       At our hospital, we utilize state-of-the-art X-ray equipment and techniques to ensure accurate 
                       and swift results while minimizing radiation exposure. Our experienced radiologists analyze 
                       these images to detect abnormalities, guide treatment decisions, and monitor progress.
                        With X-ray services readily available, we are dedicated to providing comprehensive diagnostic 
                        solutions that play a pivotal role in your healthcare journey. Whether it's for routine 
                        check-ups or more complex medical concerns, X-ray imaging is an integral part of our commitment to your well-being.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="./images/x-ray.png" alt="" height="250px">
                </div>  

        </div>
        <div class="test">
