                <div class="large">
                    Lipid Profile:
                </div>
                <p>A Lipid Profile is a diagnostic tool that evaluates your cholesterol levels and lipid content
                     in the blood. By measuring different types of cholesterol (such as HDL and LDL cholesterol)
                      and triglycerides, this test helps us assess your cardiovascular health and potential risk factors 
                      for heart disease. Understanding your lipid profile is crucial for making informed decisions about
                       dietary habits, exercise, and medical interventions that can reduce your risk of
                        heart-related complications. Whether you're proactively managing your heart health or responding to specific concerns, 
                    our hospital's advanced lipid profile analysis empowers you to take control of your well-being.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="./images/lipid.png" alt="" height="250px">
                </div>  

        </div>
        <div class="test">
            <div class="test-desc">

                <div class="large">
                    Electrocardiogram (ECG/EKG):
                </div>
                <p>An Electrocardiogram (ECG/EKG) is a vital diagnostic test that records the electrical
                     activity of your heart. This painless and non-invasive procedure helps detect irregular
                      heart rhythms (arrhythmias), assess the overall health of your heart, and identify
                       potential signs of cardiac diseases. By analyzing the patterns and waves in the ECG,
                        our experienced cardiologists can make accurate assessments of your heart's function and
                         recommend appropriate interventions to ensure your cardiovascular well-being. Whether you're seeking
                          preventive care or addressing heart-related symptoms, 
                    our hospital's ECG services provide invaluable insights into your heart's health..</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="./images/monitoring.png" alt="" height="250px">
                </div>  

        </div>
        <div class="test">
